ID:  TC_006

Title: Verify product details

Priority: High

Severity: Major

Preconditions:
- At least 1 product exist in system
- Product page accessible without login

Steps:
1. Navigate to “https://automationexercise.com/products”
2. Click "View Product" button on first product
3. Wait for product detail page to load

Expected result:
1. Navigation successful: - URL changes to /product_details/{id} - Page loads without errors
2. Product detail page displays all required information:
- Product Name (prominent and clear)
- Category (e.g., "Women > Tops")
- Price (e.g., "Rs. 500")
- Availability (In Stock / Out of Stock)
- Condition (New / Used)
- Brand name
3. Additional elements present:
- Product image(s) (not broken)
- Rating stars
- Quantity selector - "Add to cart" button (visible and enabled) 

Actual result:

Status: Not Run